As a player, I want to be able to see a scoreboard so that I can compare my performance with other players.

As a player, I want to be able to save the progress of a cryptogram so that I can come back to it later.

As a player, I want there to be a large selection of cryptograms to play so that the game has good replay value.

As a player, I want the Cryptograms to encrypt in a random way so that they are challenging to solve.

As a player, I want to be able to recieve hints so that if I am stuck I am able to move forward with the game.

As a player, I want to be able to see the solution to the cryptogram if I am unable to complete it.

As a player, I don't want a time limit so that I have all the time I need to finish the cryptogram.

As a player, I want to be able to see my percentage of successfully completed cryptograms so that I can track my progress.

As a player, I want to see how frequent each letter is in the cryptogram so that I can look for common groups of letters.

As a player, I want to be able to undo my guesses until the cryptogram is clear so that I can fix my errors.

